# 📈 RFM Analysis

## What is RFM Analysis?

RFM Analysis is a customer segmentation technique based on:

| Metric | Description |
|---|---|
| Recency | How recently customer purchased |
| Frequency | How often customer purchases |
| Monetary | How much customer spends |

---

# 👥 Customer Segments

## 🏆 Premium Customers

High Recency  
High Frequency  
High Monetary Value  

## ❤️ Loyal Customers

Frequent customers with strong engagement.

## 📈 Potential Customers

Customers with future growth potential.

## ⚠️ At Risk Customers

Customers showing declining activity.

## ❌ Lost Customers

Inactive customers with low engagement.

